channel.title: [PI] Absolutely Confused
channel.description:
Ok,
So a few hours ago my Servers was perfectly fine, it was multiplayer, people were allowed to get on, have fun, do things, then all of a sudden no one is able to login to my Server except for my IP...
I checked everything, I checked my portforwarding and Redid it, I checked my No-IP thing, I checked my internet Connection I checked EVERYTHING, but I noticed that my Hamachi says updating...
Is my Hamachi Update the problem or is it something else....?
PLEASE HELP ME. ALL HELP IS APPRECIATED.

item.title: [PI] Absolutely Confused
item.dc:creator: @zyle1992 Zymus
item.description:
@zyle1992 wrote:

First of all, remove Hamachi. No one with a basic understanding of networking uses it.

Go to canyouseeme.org and type in the port number, then click the button. If it says I can’t see you, you haven’t forwarded properly. If you have, check and see if the IPs of the other people are banned. Could be a logic bug.
